        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer224986250" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2480133163404149801">I don&apos;t usually read much historical fiction, esp. Mormon church related historical fiction b/c I really want to know what is truly documented and what has been embellished by the author. I gave this four stars b/c I think that knowing about the history of black pioneers is important and b/c the authors clearly endnoted each chapter with sources for the specifics that have been documented. The stories were kind of stilted at times-- I think it&apos;s hard to find a balance between writing a fully fle</span>
  <span id="freeText2480133163404149801" style="display:none">I don't usually read much historical fiction, esp. Mormon church related historical fiction b/c I really want to know what is truly documented and what has been embellished by the author. I gave this four stars b/c I think that knowing about the history of black pioneers is important and b/c the authors clearly endnoted each chapter with sources for the specifics that have been documented. The stories were kind of stilted at times-- I think it's hard to find a balance between writing a fully fleshed out story (which would require a lot of speculation on details) and sticking to available records without being boring or spare. I thought this was important reading and gave me a lot to think about.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2480133163404149801" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
